These are the minutes for the April 13th, 2026 SPI Board Meeting,
held at 20:00 UTC in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org.
[LOG](../../../logs/2026/2026-04-13.txt).

## President's report
<pre>
I am continuing to assist with the treasury team to ensure timely processing
of payments and reimbursements. We are also working with to prepare for
the auditing of our 2025 financial documents and federal and New York State
filings.
</pre>

## Treasurer's report

<pre>
The treasury team is continuing to process reimbursements and payments. If
there is an urgent need (i.e. other than NET 30) please let
treasurer@rt.spi-inc.org know
</pre>

## Secretary's report

<pre>
I have finally recorded 2026 Conflict of Interest declarations from all
directors, thanks again to all of you for your patience and diligence!
</pre>

